<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263447>
    dc:description "PLATE 147. Splendrillia coccinata (Reeve, 1845). Upper panel. Fig. 1: Pleurotoma coccinata Reeve, copy of Reeve’s pl. 33, fig. 299; Fig. 2: neotype, dorsal view at the same scale for comparison; Fig. 3: neotype, Chatham Bay, Union I., SVG (USNM 1291358): ventral, lateral & dorsal views. Lower panel. Figs. 4 – 7: Chatham Bay, Union I., SVG: Figs. 4, 6: USNM 1291359; Figs. 5, 7: ANSP 464958; Fig. 8, 10: Flamand Bay, Grenada (BMSM 14997); Fig. 9: Devil’s Bay, Grenada (BMSM 14997); Fig. 11: Canoe Bay, Grenada (MZSP 122074); Fig. 12: St. Georges, Grenada (UF 496646); Figs. 13 – 17: Chatham Bay, Union I., SVG: Fig. 13: USNM 1291359; Figs. 14 – 17: ANSP 464958; Fig. 18: St. Georges, Grenada (DMNH 240359); Fig. 19: Large I., Grenada (MZSP 122073); Figs. 20 – 21: S end of Baliceaux I., SVG: Fig. 20: M. Williams coll.; Fig. 21: USNM 1291360; Figs. 22 – 23: Saline I., Grenada (UF 470343); Fig. 24: Ronde I., Grenada (MZSP 122072); Figs. 25 – 27: St. Georges, Grenada: Figs. 25 – 26: UF 496646; Fig. 27: P. Stahlschmidt coll." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263447/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

